<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
    <id>10484</id>
    <title>User has to allow ALL Extended permissions passed to a login request</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">When directing a user to login to Facebook.com_ via a Desktop application; and passing a list of extended permissions via the scope parameter_ the user is asked to verify each permission individually_ however clicking  Don t Allow  on one screen re-directs the user back to the  http://www.facebook.com/connect/login_success.html _ not allowing them to continue on with the other permissions.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">The end user should be-able to not allow certain permissions but still continue to allow others.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
